name: Chemwood walk delay
matches: ^You struggle to push through \w+'s thick, swirling mists\.$
^You struggle to move with \w+'s amplified fields disrupting your muscular impulses, but you stumble determinedly in an effort to leave\.$
^\w+'s whirling leaves harry you as you try to leave, slowing your egress\.$
^You begin moving through the thick, swirling flurries of \w+'s spores\.$
You stumble through the thick smog, coughing and sputtering as you try to find cleaner air.
^You stumble around stupidly as \w+'s mind-dulling effluvia seeps into you, fighting against a strangely dull mind to make your legs take you out of here\.$
